  "body": "The error:\n\n```\nUncaught Error: Invariant Violation: addComponentAsRefTo(...): Only a ReactOwner can have refs. This usually means that you're trying to add a ref to a component that doesn't have an owner (that is, was not created inside of another component's `render` method). Try rendering this component inside of a new top-level component which will hold the ref.\n```\n\nMinimal example repository using webpack: https://github.com/brainkim/reactdomerror\nSteps to reproduce:\n\n```\ngit clone https://github.com/brainkim/reactdomerror\nnpm install\nmake build\n```\n\nspin up a http server and point to index.html\nThis error is mitigated by using the deprecated `React.render` method instead.\n",
